caption:
Every cover is a cosmic explosion of color and chaos!
These BossKong custom blank sketch variants turn comic classics into one-of-a-kind galactic grails. From mystic spellcasters to mad love and cosmic titans—every detail is hand-crafted, hyper-stylized, and straight from the multiverse.
Which one’s your favorite—Zatanna & Constantine, Harley & Joker, Silver Surfer & Galactus, or Spidey & the Hobgoblin?

BossKong Originals. One shot. One cover. No copies.
